Title: Series: Grosvenor gallery
Description: Rest on the flight into Egypt, after Barocci; the Virgin dips a bowl into a pool of water as Joseph and Jesus play with a tree branch with berries; the donkey stands at right; in oval; illustration cut from John Young's 'A Catalogue of Pictures at Grosvenor House'. 1820 Etching
Associated titles: A Catalogue of Pictures at Grosvenor House
